query:
SELECT u.id as userId, u.email, u.name, s.id as supplierId, s.companyName, su.role 
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN supplierUsers su ON u.id = su.userId 
LEFT JOIN suppliers s ON su.supplierId = s.id 
WHERE u.accountType = 'supplier' 
ORDER BY u.id DESC 
LIMIT 5;
